<div class="page_header"><span class="page_header_span">Ossiarch Bonereapers</span></div>
<div class="noprint">

</div>
<!--/noindex-->
<p class="legend ShowFluff">The Ossiarch legions are an undead force like no other. Created to be autonomous, they are trusted to enact Nagash’s will on a hundred war fronts at once. Their empire gathers war materiel from the cadavers of each battle, harvesting bone with which to create new warriors, build fortifications and begin the cycle of death over again.</p>
This page contains all of the rules you need to field your Ossiarch Bonereapers miniatures on the battlefields of the Mortal Realms, from a host of exciting allegiance abilities to a range of warscrolls and warscroll battalions. The rules are split into the following sections.<ul></ul>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;"><div class="BreakInsideAvoid Corner3" style="padding:0px;max-width:988px;"><table class="frameDark collapse" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tbody><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_1.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_2.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_3.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_8.png" style="width:20px"></td><td bgcolor="#1d190d" style="color:#fefefe"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif; font-size:1em"><div class="contents_header">Contents</div><div class="NavColumns3"><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers#Books" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>ooks</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers#Designers-Commentary" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">D</b>esigners’ Commentary</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers#Battletome:-Ossiarch-Bonereapers" style="color:#fefefe">Battletome: Ossiarch Bonereapers</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers/#Allies" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>llies</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers/#Battle-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attle Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/ossiarch-bonereapers/#Lords-of-the-Ossiarch-Empire" style="color:#fefefe">Lords of the Ossiarch Empire</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span